多得你班仆街"},{"pid":"f37b694316a41718674bf63c9387b660ba9a28b2","tid":1665908,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:33:25.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭教鍾意和平只係鳩up<br />\n同耶撚不共戴天 <br />\n一講以色列就會反面"},{"pid":"8b31fb33aa4de2038e13713dc89aca512e12f6b9","tid":1665908,"uid":88985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:33:57.000Z","msg":"推，全世界都要睇"},{"pid":"3e824aacfac39c3981b3e9a30b83d01c7cf0ee7d","tid":1665908,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2c880fe82ec6aee474737e68e25f18b23fcbab","tid":1665908,"uid":151525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:36:27.000Z","msg":"學到嘢"},{"pid":"92dc54c6572ea35fe69ed72406cdc64ba848faad","tid":1665908,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:37:42.000Z","msg":"我地同黑警唔同，我地識尊重，唔好再講isis"},{"pid":"92ea97250d9232ee9cc692426d01a76e6edefa98","tid":1665908,"uid":278085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:39:27.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52820303eec9756a2f079d0c9fef677b5e30dfd2","tid":1665908,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:39:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63976a2929019afaef009659109a60d4b24cf3d0","tid":1665908,"uid":110579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"文宣要做之前都要睇埋清真寺代表記者會，好似話今日會開"},{"pid":"758d6e21391625aa24aa19abe8d0fc21030cdc40","tid":1